---
title: Honey Beef Rump & Pearl Couscous Bowl with Dill-Parsley Mayonnaise
description: Who doesn’t love the signature combo of honey and succulent beef. With tender pearls of Israeli couscous to soak
up all the flavour and a herby hit of dill-parsley mayonnaise, it'll make for a meal that you won’t be able to resist!

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
